title: Wedding Area Map
name: Wedding Area Map
description:
A Map by Anthonyandamanda

This map shows key locations and attractions for guests of the Carter-Smith Wedding on June 17, 2006 in Houston Texas.

properties.name: Frenchies
properties.description: Posted by Anthonyandamanda1041 Nasa road one, houston, texasAnthony and Amanda\'s Favorite place for Italian! Try the Caesar salad and ask for the NY Strip with Gorganzola Cheese(probably not on the menu). This restaurant is owned by the same people as Villa Capri.

properties.name: Hilton Houston NASA Clear Lake
properties.description: Posted by Anthonyandamanda3000 NASA Road One, houston, texasThere are rooms blocked off for the wedding at the Hilton. There are boat and jet ski rentals available near this location.

properties.name: Houston Hobby Airport
properties.description: Posted by AnthonyandamandaHouston Hobby Airport.

properties.name: Ichibon Japanese Restaurant
properties.description: Posted by Anthonyandamanda 406 Texas Ave, Kemah, TX 77565A good spot for Sushi and Hibachi.

properties.name: Kemah Boardwalk
properties.description: Posted by AnthonyandamandaBradford ave & 2nd street, kemah, texasThis location contains restaurants and carnival rides.

properties.name: Lone Star Flight Museum
properties.description: Posted by Anthonyandamanda 2002 Terminal Drive, Galveston, TX 77554This location is an airplane museum with restored military planes. If you love WWII planes, this is for you!

properties.name: Pappadeaux's Restaurant
properties.description: Posted by Anthonyandamanda 309 Waterfront, seabrook, texasThis is the location for the Rehersal Dinner.

properties.name: Samurai Japanese Steak & Sushi House

properties.name: Space Center Houston
properties.description: Posted by Anthonyandamanda1601 nasa road one, houston, texasTours of the Johnson Space Center are available at this location.
